The paper deals with the analysis of signal propagation and gradient backpropagation in neural networks, specifically in the context of batch normalization. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). However, since the focus is primarily on the theoretical analysis of neural networks, the first two categories are the most likely.
